# Coding Compatibility

- Prefer `NavigationLayout`, `TablePageLayout`, `SearchBar`, `DataTable`, and `DialogWrapper` before adding new page scaffolding.
- Keep route names, sample data, and UI copy generic.
- Do not reintroduce Support-specific business terms into the starter.
- If workflow guidance changes, update `docs/` first and keep this file minimal.
